      <title>中国债券收益率跌至历史低位，干预成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-bond-yields-sink-to-record-low-with-intervention-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国债券交易员无视干预迹象，将主权债券收益率推至历史低位，为与试图抑制债务飙升的当局的摊牌奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-bond-yields-sink-to-record-low-with-intervention-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
